short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Creates a BibTeX entry corresponding to a page.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Chrome extension allows you to quickly grab the BibTeX entry of the paper you are currently viewing in Chrome. It is compatible with a wide range of websites ranging from ArXiv to IEEEXplore.
